## Router Activation
The router was configured and activated using Cisco Packet Tracer CLI commands.

### Steps
1. Entered privileged and global configuration modes.
2. Assigned an IP address to FastEthernet0/1.
3. Used `no shutdown` to bring the interface up.
4. Verified connectivity with `show ip interface brief`.

### Result
Router interface FastEthernet0/1 is up/up and communicating with the switch.
